==Korean==

===Noun===
'''바람''' (baram) 

# [[wind]], [[air]], [[draft]] 
# [[fickleness]]
# (obsolete) [[wall]], [[enclosure]], [[surrounding]]  cf. [[paradise]] from Greek [[παράδεισος]] (''paradeisos'' of Persian origin, probably cognate with ''peri + teichos'' "surrounding wall")

====Derived terms====
* 바람에 (baram-e) on the [[verge]], by virtue, under the [[circumstances]] (of something)
* 바람[[벽]] (baram-byeog, -byeok) [[wall]], [[enclosure]]

====Related terms====
* [[바라다]] (barada) To [[desire]], [[expect]], [[hope]], [[want]]; (obsolete) [[rely]]
* 바라[[보다]] (bara-boda) To [[look out]], [[look over]] 
* 바라[[지다]] (bara-jida) To [[widen]], [[open]]
* [[바래다]] (baraeda) To [[see off]], [[send off]]
* 바래[[주다]] (barae-juda) To [[see off]], [[send off]]
* [[바램]] (baraem) [[desire]], [[expectation]], [[hope]]

